title: Your Horoscope and Spirit Kylie Jenner for the Week of October 11
text:
~*~LiBrA~*~ A lot of unexpected things are in the air this week, and you love a good surprise! You could meet someone who sparks your interest Sunday so say yes to a last-minute game day party. The new moon in your sign Monday feels like a breath of fresh air and you are poised to get to a whole new level at work in the next few weeks. Someone you meet at the gym or during a quiet picnic in the park this weekend could bring out the true romantic in you. Try dating someone who appeals to your more contemplative side! A very positive — and unanticipated — family situation could also unfold this week, so if Great Aunt Milly randomly reaches out for your birthday, make it a priority to reconnect. ​
 Spirit Kylie Jenner

GIF Your Horoscope and Spirit Nate Archibald for the... GIF Your Horoscope and ​Spirit Serena Van Der Woodsen... ~*~ScOrPiO~*~ ​ ​This week may feel like a bit of a mixed bag, Scorpio. You like to be in control of the situation but there may be some unexpected surprises that pop up, especially related to travel or communications. Try not to make too many assumptions about the situation since things are still unfolding. But your instincts will be strong on Monday's new moon, so pay attention. An attraction to a friend could reach fever pitch by this weekend! If you two are truly meant to be, now is the time to let yourself get carried away by your feelings rather than trying to micromanage the situation. Saturday is an all-star day when your crew really comes through for you, so make time to all hang out together. ​
​Spirit Kylie Jenner ​
GIF Share Tweet Pin E-mail E!/ Lauren Ahn ~*~SaGiTtArIuS~*~ ​ ​This is shaping up to be an amazing week for you, Sagittarius! Getting to know new people could lead to an unexpected break Sunday, so get out there and socialize! It could also lead to a love connection. And your bond with your friends is stronger than ever after Monday's new moon, so plan a group dinner in the next few weeks. An opposition between creative Venus and mystical Neptune on Friday will be ultra-inspiring for you. You could brainstorm your next great idea or fall for someone you work with. Be open to how you feel since this could be epic! And follow your gut about financial matters as far as work is concerned. ​
Spirit Kylie Jenner ​
GIF Share Tweet Pin E-mail E!/ Lauren Ahn ~*~CaPrIcOrN~*~ ​A lot of positive changes are happing right now, Capricorn. An unexpected family drama could crop up Sunday but you have all the answers you need about how to deal with it. Monday's new moon in Libra could start you on a whole new chapter of your career. People you meet now will be ultra-influential, so have fun mixing business with pleasure. A getaway this weekend could prove to be super romantic. If you and your love can escape, you will have some experiences you will never forget! And to top it all off, a long-held dream is one big step closer to reality. ​
​ ​
​Spirit Kylie Jenner ​
